    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_5946552681012004283.png",
                "id": "talent68224",
                "key": "冰螢稜錐",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰螢稜錐"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰螢</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/1a979041a9881649ba69332b20dd5820_4195977603139593267.png",
                "id": "talent56436",
                "key": "霧虛搖喚",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "霧虛搖喚"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成5點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，本角色<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">附著冰元素</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">流螢護罩</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">流螢護罩</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>為我方出戰角色提供<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">1點護盾</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">創建時：</span>如果我方場上存在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰螢</span>，則額外提供其<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span>（最多額外提供3點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/8d60085e1f79ee9a2bb87006d7f2d32c_5319901925368690240.png",
                "id": "talent89733",
                "key": "冰枝白花",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰枝白花"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span>（可疊加，至多疊加3層）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">愚人眾·冰螢術士「普通攻擊」後：</span>此牌<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">愚人眾·冰螢術士受到發生元素反應的傷害後：</span>此牌<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>-1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7437701543041405114.png",
                "id": "talent45112",
                "key": "冰螢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/1467dd7dd3fec80047e77cc996621508_52791988157413238.png",
                "title": "冰螢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著冰元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到物理或火元素傷害後提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_3647573814981649048.png",
                "id": "talent50656",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>不透過傷害附著冰元素時，發生的元素反應會忽略傷害效果：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：沒有效果</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：沒有效果</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：使目標本回合無法行動（受到物理或火元素傷害後提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_9166043469325561511.png",
                "id": "talent38568",
                "key": "附著冰元素",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "附著冰元素"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span></strong></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8238730171175092034.png",
